# CEREBRO needs NO secret env vars.
#
# - LLM:   Claude Code on the machine (`claude -p`) — uses its own login
# - X:     bird reads the x.com cookie from Firefox/Chrome
# - Gmail: gws uses its own Google OAuth
#
# The only sensitive value (the ntfy topic) lives in config/settings.yaml (gitignored).
# This file is kept as a placeholder; there is nothing to fill in.
